					<item>
		<title>170</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=23496</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:23:40 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/170/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with request for fuller, better-shaped breasts. &nbsp;She also had a significant amount of scoliosis which had to be accounted for. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed<a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-augmentation/"> breast augmentation</a> with silicone gel implants placed beneath the muscle. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post op. &nbsp;Note that scoliosis can cause a significant amount of asymmetry in the chest wall which often has to be taken into account when doing breast augmentation.<br />
<br />
Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel - 375cc Moderate Plus<br />
Placement: &nbsp;Subpectoral<br />
Incision: &nbsp;Inframammary		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>125</title>

				This patient presented with significant hypoplastic breasts (underdevelopment). &nbsp;After options were discussed, Dr. Truong performed breast augmentation using saline implants. &nbsp;An accessory nipple was also removed from her left nipple.<br />
<br />
<strong>Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Saline 250cc&nbsp;<br />

Incision: &nbsp;Inframammary</strong><br />
1 month post-op		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>124</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=23608</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:24:43 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/124/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented requesting breast augmentation, but was concerned about her pacemaker which was implanted in her upper left chest. &nbsp;Dr. Truong carefully performed a <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-augmentation/">breast augmentation</a> placing the implants sub-pectorally to avoid touching the pacemaker. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post-op with no affect to her pacemaker.<br />
<br />
<strong>Implant: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 375cc MPP<br />
Placement: &nbsp;Sub-pectoral<br />
Incision: &nbsp;inframammary</strong>		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>101</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=23661</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:25:12 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/101/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with breast atrophy and ptosis (drooping) after multiple pregnancies and breast feeding. &nbsp;The patient is a candidate for a <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-lift/">breast lift</a>, but decided she wanted a more natural look without the excess scars. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a simple <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-augmentation/">breast augmentation</a> with silicone gel implants. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post op and is happy with her natural-appearing breasts.<br />
<br />
&nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>58</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=23701</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:25:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/58/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with breast atrophy following breast feeding and requested restoration of breast fullness. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed bilateral <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-augmentation/">breast augmentation</a> with silicone gel implants. &nbsp;Note the patient has mild asymmetry with her right nipple being slightly lower than her left pre-operatively. &nbsp;Although more severe asymmetries can be corrected with unilateral mastopexy, mild asymmtries are usually acceptable and can be made less noticable after simple augmentation.<br />
<br />
<strong>Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 375cc Moderate Plus<br />
Placement: &nbsp;Sub-Pectoral<br />
Incision: &nbsp;Inframammary&nbsp;</strong>		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>352</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=23794</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:26:34 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/352/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with breast ptosis and abdominal laxity with excess skin post pregnancy. &nbsp;She requested smaller breasts and to correct her abominal area. &nbsp;She underwent a &quot;Mommy Makeover&quot; which consisted of a breast reduction/lift, with implants, followed by a full tummy tuck (abdominoplasty).		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>46</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=23864</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:27:26 +0000</pubDate>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with moderate ptosis and deflation of her breasts following multiple pregnancies and breast-feeding. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed an <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-lift/">augmentation mastopexy</a> &nbsp;(breast-lift with implant placement). &nbsp;The patient also underwent a full tummy tuck as part of her <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/body/mommy-makeover/">mommy makeover</a>. &nbsp;<br />
<br />
Incision: &nbsp;vertical mastopexy<br />
Placement: &nbsp;post-pectoral<br />
Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 325cc		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>14</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=23876</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:27:39 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/14/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with ptosis (drooping) of her breasts following pregnancy and breast feeding. &nbsp;To avoid extensive scarring, Dr. Truong performed an <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-lift/">Augmenation Mastopexy</a> (Breast Lift with implants) using a Benelli Mastopexy which is a technique that only leaves a minimal scar around the edge of the areola without need for the vertical lollipop or anchor scar. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[
						]]></excerpt:encoded>

		<title>245</title>

				This patient presented with deflation and ptosis (drooping) of the breast following pregnancy and breast-feeding. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a breast lift with implants (augmentation <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-lift/">mastopexy</a>), and corrected some pre-existing asymmetry. &nbsp;Of note, the patient had significant pre-existing scoliosis contributing to the asymmetry. &nbsp;The patient is 6 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>200</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=23977</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:28:58 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/200-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with severely ptotic (droopy) breasts and significant asymmetry following breast feeding. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed an Augmentation <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-lift/">Mastopexy</a>, or Breast Lift with Implants in order to correct the ptosis, add fullness, and correct asymmetry. &nbsp;The patient is seen here only 3 months post op with continued improvement expected.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>14</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=24010</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:29:29 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/14-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with ptosis (drooping) of her breasts following pregnancy and breast feeding. &nbsp;To avoid extensive scarring, Dr. Truong performed an <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-lift/">Augmenation Mastopexy</a> (Breast Lift with implants) using a Benelli Mastopexy which is a technique that only leaves a minimal scar around the edge of the areola without need for the vertical lollipop or anchor scar. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>49</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=24180</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:32:02 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/49/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with common changes that occurred after multiple &nbsp;pregnancies and breast feeding. &nbsp;She had severe ptosis (drooping) of her breasts as well as atrophy (deflation), and asymmetry (uneveness). &nbsp;She also had a significant amount of skin laxity, stretchmarks, and diastatsis (weakness of the tissue between the muscles) of her abdominal area. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/mommy-makeover/">Mommy Makeover</a> which consisted of an <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/breast/breast-lift/">Augmentation Mastopexy</a> (breast lift with implants), correction of her asymmetery, a full <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/body/tummy-tuck/">Tummy Tuck</a>, and repair of the muscle diastasis. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>352</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=24295</link>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/352-4/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented with breast ptosis and abdominal laxity with excess skin post pregnancy. &nbsp;She requested smaller breasts and to correct her abominal area. &nbsp;She underwent a &quot;Mommy Makeover&quot; which consisted of a breast reduction/lift, with implants, followed by a full tummy tuck (abdominoplasty).		]]></content:encoded>

				This patient presented requesting body re-shaping with thinning of the waist and enlarging the buttocks. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/body/brazilian-butt-lift/">Brazilian Butt Lift</a> procedure in which liposuction and fat harvest was done in the upper lower abdomen, as well as the flank and back areas. &nbsp;The patient&#39;s fat was then purified and re-injected into the buttocks as a fat transplant. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 8 months after the procedure.		]]></content:encoded>

		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient underwent a <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/body/brazilian-butt-lift/">Brazilian Butt Lift</a> by Dr. Truong. &nbsp;Liposuction was performed in the abdomen, flanks, and back areas and the purified fat was transferred to the buttocks using injection technique. &nbsp;500cc of fat was re-injected into each buttock.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>112</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=25701</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:50:58 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/112/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient desired fuller buttocks. &nbsp;After options were discussed, the patient opted for a natural augmentation with her own fat tissue. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/body/brazilian-butt-lift/">Brazilian Butt Lift</a> in which fat is transfered from her abdomen, waist, thighs, flanks, and back into her buttocks. &nbsp;The result is a fuller, yet natural augmentation of the buttocks. &nbsp;The patient is seen here one month post op.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>105</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=25706</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:51:01 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>

		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient presented after multiple treatments with silicone injections into her buttocks which was done elsewhere. &nbsp;Dr. Truong does not recommend injection of any foreign substances like silicone for buttock augmentation. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a &quot;<a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/body/brazilian-butt-lift/">Brazilian Butt Lift</a>&quot; in which the patient&#39;s own fat is harvested, purified, and re-injected into the buttocks for a safer and more natural augmentation.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>327</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/labiaplasty-lithotomy-view/327/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:02:37 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/327/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient underwent traumatic tear of her labia minora during child-birth many years prior.  She underwent reconstructive repair and "Turkish Moon" labiaplasty by Dr. Kafali with a great cosmetic result.		]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[

		<title>209</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/gynecomastia/209/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:07:41 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/209/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient was unhappy with his protruding nipples. &nbsp;After evaluation he was deemed to have idiopathic gynecomastia. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed his signature gynecomastia procedure using SmartLipo chest sculpting, plus laser skin tightening, as well as direct gland excision. &nbsp;The patient is only 1 month post op. &nbsp;Notice a resolution of the nipple projection and a more masculine chest contour.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>177</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/gynecomastia/177/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:07:49 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/177/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient had moderate gynecomastia with enlarged nipples since puberty. &nbsp;He is very fit and wanted a more masculine look to the nipple area. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed his signature gynecomastia procedure using SmartLipo of the chest with skin tightening and direct gland excision to remove the breast tissue. &nbsp;Note the automatic shrinkage of the nipples once the breast tissue is removed. &nbsp;No nipple reduction was necessary. &nbsp;The patient is seen here only 1 week post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>149</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/gynecomastia/149/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:08:28 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/149/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severe gynecomastia (enlargement of male breasts.) &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed gynecomastia reduction surgery using Smart Lipo laser lipolysis of the chest followed by subcutaneous mastectomy through a nipple incision. &nbsp;The patient is seen here only 3 months post-op with excellent result. &nbsp;Due to the significant skin retraction from the Smart Lipo, he will not need any additional skin excision. &nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>44</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/gynecomastia/44/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:09:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/44/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This athletic patient had minimal gynecomastia but was unhappy with his mild nipple protrusion which did not improve with chest excercises. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed Smart Lipo to sculpt the lower chest area as well as abdominal area followed by with direct excision of the breast glands. &nbsp;The result is subtle, but the patient is very happy that there is no nipple protrusion at all when he flexes his pectoralis muscles. &nbsp;Also note the natural shrinking of the areola after the procedure. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>

		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/149-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severe gynecomastia (enlargement of male breasts.) &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed gynecomastia reduction surgery using Smart Lipo laser lipolysis of the chest followed by subcutaneous mastectomy through a nipple incision. &nbsp;The patient is seen here only 3 months post-op with excellent result. &nbsp;Due to the significant skin retraction from the Smart Lipo, he will not need any additional skin excision. &nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>44</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/male-smart-lipo/44-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:10:16 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/44-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This athletic patient had minimal gynecomastia but was unhappy with his mild nipple protrusion which did not improve with chest excercises. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed Smart Lipo to sculpt the lower chest area as well as abdominal area followed by with direct excision of the breast glands. &nbsp;The result is subtle, but the patient is very happy that there is no nipple protrusion at all when he flexes his pectoralis muscles. &nbsp;Also note the natural shrinking of the areola after the procedure. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>12</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/male-smart-lipo/12-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:10:26 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/12-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				31 year old male with moderate to severe male gynecomastia. &nbsp;After pt. underwent full work-up was diagnosed with idiopathic gynecomastia. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed Smart Lipo chest sculpting, followed by direct excision of a significant amount of breast tissue. &nbsp;The patient is shown here 2 months post-op. &nbsp;Notice the areolas have also naturally shrunken in diameter. &nbsp;There is mild bruising, but result is a more sculpted, masculine chest contour. &nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>3</title>

		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient complained of heaviness in her upper eyelids, and corneal irritation from down-ward pointing eyelashes. &nbsp;She underwent an Asian Eyelid Surgery which created an upper eyelid crease to turn the eyelashes upward. &nbsp;The result is a natural appearing double upper eyelid with resolution of corneal irritation.		]]></content:encoded>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This gentleman presented with primary concern of &quot;bags&quot; under his eyes which he felt made him look tired. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a subciliary lower blepharoplasty with removal of fatty tissue and excess skin. &nbsp;The result is a subtle improvement in the bags, without drastically changing the gentleman&#39;s natural appearance. &nbsp;This gentleman may also benefit from laser resurfacing to improve the fine lines.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>160</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/eyelid-surgery/160/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:15:15 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/160/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient had previous blepharoplasty done a few years prior. &nbsp;She presented complaining of residual loose skin on her lower eyelids. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a revision lower blepharoplasty via subcilliary approach.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>4</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/eyelid-surgery/4/</link>

		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient complained of skin laxity of her lower eyelid area and was also found to have a dropped mid-face fat pad. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a lower blepharoplasty &nbsp;with removal of redundant skin, as well as a suspension of the malar fat pad to lift the cheeks. &nbsp;The result is a very natural rejuvenation of the lower eyelid and cheek area.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>401</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/earlobe-repair/401/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:16:32 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/401/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient had very large earlobe guages that he wished to close. &nbsp;Dr. Truong perfomed his specially-designed earlobe repair procedure in which the guage holes are completely removed, and the earlobe reconstructed and re-attached for a natural appearance. &nbsp;Once healed, there will be no evidence of the prior guages. &nbsp;The patient is 3 month post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>275</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/earlobe-repair/275/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:16:43 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/275/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[
				This patient had very large earlobe guages that he wished to close. &nbsp;Dr. Truong perfomed his specially-designed earlobe repair procedure in which the guage holes are completely removed, and the earlobe reconstructed and re-attached for a natural appearance. &nbsp;Once healed, there will be no evidence of the prior guages. &nbsp;The patient is 1 month post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>55</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/earlobe-repair/55/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:16:58 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/55/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severely stretched earlobes from ear guages. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed earlobe repair using a special technique in which the entire stretched lobe is removed and a new earlobe is reconstructed. &nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[
						]]></excerpt:encoded>

		<wp:post_date><![CDATA[2019-04-02 11:16:58]]></wp:post_date>
		<wp:post_date_gmt><![CDATA[2019-04-02 11:16:58]]></wp:post_date_gmt>

					<item>
		<title>235</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/precision-tx-lazer-lift/235-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:17:04 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/235-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient had Precision Tx treatment by Dr. Truong to define her lower face and jawline. &nbsp;Precision Tx uses a special Smart Lipo laser fiber specifically designed to melt fat and tighten skin in the lower face, neck, and chink area. &nbsp;The patient is 4 months post op with continued improvement anticipated.		]]></content:encoded>

						]]></excerpt:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>300</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/300/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:20:16 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/300/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[This patient presented with severely hypoplastic breasts.  Because she is a professional body builder, Dr. Truong recommended placing the implants ABOVE the muscle in the sub-glandular plane.  She is seen here 3 months post-op with an excellent result.

Implants:  Mentor Memory Gel 375cc High Profile
Sub-glandular
Inframammary incision.]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>215</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/215/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:21:26 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/215/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient had breast atrophy (deflation) and pseudo-ptosis following pregnancy and breast-feeding. &nbsp; The patient declined a lift due to the incisions required. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a breast augmentation with Memory gel implants. &nbsp;The patient still has a small degree of pseudoptosis (laxity of the lower breast), but is very happy with her result.<br />
<br />
&nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>211</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/211/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:21:56 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/211/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with very common deflation or &quot;atrophy&quot; of her breasts following pregnancy and breast-feeding. &nbsp;She did not require a lift and Dr. Truong performed breast augmentation with Memory Gel implants placed beneath the muscle.<br />
<br />
Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 350cc MPP<br />
Incision: &nbsp;inframammary<br />
Placement: &nbsp;Post pectoral<br />
6 months postop		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>194</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/194/</link>

		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented requesting fuller breasts. &nbsp;She had good pre-existing antatomy and breast shape. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed breast augmentation with Memory Gel implants placed beneath the muscle. &nbsp;The patient is 8 months post-op<br />
<br />
<strong>Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 375cc MPP<br />
Incision: &nbsp;Inframammary<br />

					<item>
		<title>180</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/180/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:23:09 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/180/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented requesting enlargement of her breasts. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a Breast Augmentation with silicone gel implants. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post-op.<br />
<br />
Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 375cc Moderate Plus Profile<br />
Placement: &nbsp;Subpectoral<br />
Incision: &nbsp;Inframammary<br />

					<item>
		<title>172</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/172/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:23:24 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/172/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented requesting fuller breasts. &nbsp;Although here breasts were small and low-lying, they had good shape and symmetry. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed Breast Augmentation with silicone gel implants beneath the muscle. &nbsp;Note that implants can make breasts larger and fuller up top, but they do not raise the breasts at all. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 1 year post op and is very happy with her results.<br />
<br />
Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 400cc Moderate Plus<br />
Placement: &nbsp;Subpectoral<br />
Incision: &nbsp;Inframammary<br />
&nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>150</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/150/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:23:57 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/150/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with post-partum changes including breast atrophy (deflation of the breasts), abdominal skin and muscle laxity (looseness), and significant straie (stretch marks). &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a &quot;Mommy Makeover&quot; surgery which included a full tummy tuck with muscle repair and breast augmentation with Mentor Memory Gel implants placed beneath the muscle. &nbsp;The patient is seen here only 3 months post-op with very dramatic results.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>139</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/139/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:24:23 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/139/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with a prior Breast Augmentation by another surgeon. &nbsp;She was unhappy with the size and placement of the implants, feeling that they were too small and placed too high, which gave her breasts a &quot;conical&quot; appearance. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a Breast Revision in which he replaced the implants with Memory Gel implants, lowered to the pocket to fill the lower pole of the breasts, and released the muscles medially to allow for better cleavage. &nbsp;<strong>Notice in profile how the breast has a much more gentle and natural slope.</strong> &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>113</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/113/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:25:04 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/113/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with significant breast atrophy (shrinkage) and asymmetry following multiple pregnancies and breast feeding. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed Breast Augmentation with silicone Memory Gel Implants. &nbsp;The patient opted not to undergo a unilateral mastopexy to correct her pre-existing areolar asymmetry and the resullt was satisfactory to her post-op.<br />
<br />
<strong>Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 400cc Moderate Plus<br />
Incision: &nbsp;Inframammary<br />
Placement: &nbsp;Post-Pectoral</strong><br />
&nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>89</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/89/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:25:17 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/89/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This young patient presented with hypoplastic (underdeveloped) breasts with enlarged areolas due to tuberous breast development. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a breast augmentation with Saline implants. &nbsp;The patient chose not to undergo areolar reduction. &nbsp;She is seen here 3 months post-op.<br />
<strong>Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Saline Implants - Fill to 420cc<br />
Placement: &nbsp;Sub-Pectoral<br />
Incision: &nbsp;Inframammary&nbsp;</strong>		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>88</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation/88/</link>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with hypoplastic (under-developed) breasts. &nbsp;Note the deficiency of breast tissue int he lower aspect of the breast. &nbsp;Dr. Truong designed a breast augmentation to lower the inframammary crease and create more fullness in the lower poles of the breast for a more aesthetically pleasing-shaped breast. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post-op.<br />

					<item>
		<title>47</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-lift/47/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:27:17 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/47/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with moderate ptosis (drooping) of the breasts with enlarged areolas. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a vertical augmentation mastopexy (breast lift with implant placement) to correct these issues. &nbsp;The result is a lifted breasts with more fullness in the upper poles and smaller areolas giving an overall more youthful appearance to the breasts. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post-op.<br />
<br />
Placement: &nbsp;post-pectoral<br />
Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 375cc high profile.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>208</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation-revision/208/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:27:47 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/208/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient was unhappy with her breast augmentation done a few years back by another surgeon. &nbsp;The implants were too small for her tall frame and the inframammary creases were uneven. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a revision using Mentor Memory Gel implants in a larger size, and revised her inframammary crease in order to achieve a more proportionate aestheticially pleasing result. &nbsp;Her pre-exisiting nipple height asymmetry did not bother the patient and she opted not to address it. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>140</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation-revision/140-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:28:05 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/140-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient had a prior Breast Augmentation and presented with capsular contracture and non-decent of her implants. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a Revision of her Breast Augmentation with a Mastopexy (Breast Lift) in which he was able to preserve her existing implants. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post-op. &nbsp;Her scars from the mastopexy will continue to fade.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>139</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation-revision/139-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:28:12 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/139-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with a prior Breast Augmentation by another surgeon. &nbsp;She was unhappy with the size and placement of the implants, feeling that they were too small and placed too high, which gave her breasts a &quot;conical&quot; appearance. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a Breast Revision in which he replaced the implants with Memory Gel implants, lowered to the pocket to fill the lower pole of the breasts, and released the muscles medially to allow for better cleavage. &nbsp;<strong>Notice in profile how the breast has a much more gentle and natural slope.</strong> &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>129</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation-revision/129/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:28:17 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/129/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with dissatisfaction over her previous breast augmentation which was performed through the axilla (underarm) using very small saline implants. &nbsp;She requested fuller breasts with more &quot;cleavage&quot;. &nbsp;Dr. performed a Breast Revision by removing the old implants, performing a capsulectormy and creating a new pocket. &nbsp;Finally, more appropriately-sized Memory Gel implants were placed. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post op much more satisfied with her result. &nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>Implants: &nbsp;Mentor Memory Gel 425cc HP</strong>		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>91</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation-revision/91/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:28:25 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/91/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with bilateral capsular contracture of her breast implants placed by another surgeon 10 years previously. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a breast revision with capsulotomies (releasing of scar tissue) of both breasts and replacement of implants to Memory Gel implants. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>9</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation-revision/9/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:28:27 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/9/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				<span style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #333333;">This patient had a prior </span>Breast Augmentation<span style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #333333;"> and developed severe asymmetry with capsular contracture and bottoming out of her implants.  Her prior implants were saline and were placed inappropriately above the muscle.  Using a special technique with a synthetic mesh, Dr. Truong converted her pocket to below the muscle, removed the old capsule, and replaced her implants with Mentor Memory Gel implants.  Dr. Truong is an expert on Breast Augmentation revision.</span>		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>150</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/mommy-makeover/150-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:31:39 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/150-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with post-partum changes including breast atrophy (deflation of the breasts), abdominal skin and muscle laxity (looseness), and significant straie (stretch marks). &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a &quot;Mommy Makeover&quot; surgery which included a full tummy tuck with muscle repair and breast augmentation with Mentor Memory Gel implants placed beneath the muscle. &nbsp;The patient is seen here only 3 months post-op with very dramatic results.		]]></content:encoded>

		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with typical post-pregnancy changes of breast atrophy (deflation), and loose skin and stretch marks around the abdominal area. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a complete Mommy Makeover with breast augmentation followed by a full tummy tuck. &nbsp;Note the belly button was off-center pre-operatively, which was corrected with umbilicoplasty. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>50</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/mommy-makeover/50/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:31:53 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/50/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with a very severe case of rectus diastasis (weakness of the tissue connecting the abdominal muscles), and a large umbilical hernia as a result of multiple pregnancies. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a full Tummy Tuck with repair of her diastasis and repair of her umbilical hernia, as well as umbilicoplasty. &nbsp;To complete her Mommy Makeover, she also had an Augmentation Mastopexy (breast lift with implants). &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>21</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/mommy-makeover/21/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:32:12 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/21/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severe abdominal laxity and excess skin following pregnancy and significant weight loss. &nbsp;Even though here abdominal muscles were well-developed, they were covered with excess skin which the patient could not improve with exercise. &nbsp;She also had a low vertical midline scar from an emergency C-section. &nbsp;Dr. Truong perforemd his signature abdominoplasty with rectus muscle tightening, and recreation of a natural belly button. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post-op with an incredible transformation. &nbsp;She also underwent modest breast augmentation to complete her Mommy Makeover.]]></content:encoded>

		<title>338</title>

		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/338/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severe rectus diastasis, hernia, skin laxity, and stretch marks from multiple pregnancies.  Dr. Truong tightened and reconstructed her abdominal area with his signature Tummy Tuck including rectus muscle plication and natural umbilicoplasty with hernia repair.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>309</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/full-tummy-tuck/309-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:34:47 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/309-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severe abdominal laxity, rectus diastasis, and umbilical hernia following multiple pregnancies.  Dr. Truong performed his signature Tummy Tuck with rectus diastasis and hernia repair for a dramatic transformation.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>204</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/full-tummy-tuck/204/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:35:50 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/204/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented following an unsuccessful &quot;tummy tuck&quot; that was performed in Vietnam. &nbsp;Apparently, the previous surgeon only performed a partial abdominoplasty in which only some excess skin was removed. &nbsp;Despite the long, high-riding, unsightly scar, there was minimal improvement of the abdominal shape and contour. &nbsp;<br />
Dr. Truong performed a revision converting to a full traditional abdominoplasty in which he repaired the abdominal muscles, as well as removing additional excess skin and fat, and reconstructed the belly button. &nbsp;Note that the scar was only slightly lengthened, but the final result is a proper reconstruction of her body shape. &nbsp;The patient is 4 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>150</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/full-tummy-tuck/150-3/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:37:22 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/150-3/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with post-partum changes including breast atrophy (deflation of the breasts), abdominal skin and muscle laxity (looseness), and significant straie (stretch marks). &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a &quot;Mommy Makeover&quot; surgery which included a full tummy tuck with muscle repair and breast augmentation with Mentor Memory Gel implants placed beneath the muscle. &nbsp;The patient is seen here only 3 months post-op with very dramatic results.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>94</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/full-tummy-tuck/94/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:37:43 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/94/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with excess loose skin, fatty tissue, and muscle bulging of the abdominal area. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a full Tummy Tuck (Abdominoplasty) with removal of excess skin, fat, and tightening of the abdominal muscles as well as re-creation of the belly button. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>87</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/full-tummy-tuck/87-2/</link>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with typical post-pregnancy changes of breast atrophy (deflation), and loose skin and stretch marks around the abdominal area. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a complete Mommy Makeover with breast augmentation followed by a full tummy tuck. &nbsp;Note the belly button was off-center pre-operatively, which was corrected with umbilicoplasty. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>60</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/full-tummy-tuck/60/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:37:53 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/60/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severe abdominal laxity with excess skin and bulging of the rectus muscles (diastasis) after multiple pregnancies and significant weight loss. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a full abdominoplasty with repair of the abdominal muscles, removal of excess skin and fat, followed by re-creaation of a natural-appearing belly button (umbilicoplasty). &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post-op. &nbsp;Notice the complete transfomation of her mid-section and body shape. &nbsp;The improvement can even be seen in the posterior view. &nbsp; The scar is easily hidden in the natural string bikini line.		]]></content:encoded>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severe skin laxity, abdominal muscle bulging, and significant stretch marks - all very common changes that occur as a result of multiple pregnancies. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a full Abdominoplasty (Tummy Tuck) with removal of excess skin and fat, repair of the muscle bulge, and creation of a new belly button. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post op. &nbsp;Note a complete transformation of her body contour.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>149</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/gynecomastia/149-3/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:43:52 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/149-3/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with severe gynecomastia (enlargement of male breasts.) &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed gynecomastia reduction surgery using Smart Lipo laser lipolysis of the chest followed by subcutaneous mastectomy through a nipple incision. &nbsp;The patient is seen here only 3 months post-op with excellent result. &nbsp;Due to the significant skin retraction from the Smart Lipo, he will not need any additional skin excision. &nbsp;		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>44</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/smartlipo/44-3/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:44:19 +0000</pubDate>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/44-3/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This athletic patient had minimal gynecomastia but was unhappy with his mild nipple protrusion which did not improve with chest excercises. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed Smart Lipo to sculpt the lower chest area as well as abdominal area followed by with direct excision of the breast glands. &nbsp;The result is subtle, but the patient is very happy that there is no nipple protrusion at all when he flexes his pectoralis muscles. &nbsp;Also note the natural shrinking of the areola after the procedure. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 3 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>229</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/brazilian-butt-lift/229-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:50:26 +0000</pubDate>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/229-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented requesting body re-shaping with thinning of the waist and enlarging the buttocks. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a Brazilian Butt Lift procedure in which liposuction and fat harvest was done in the upper lower abdomen, as well as the flank and back areas. &nbsp;The patient&#39;s fat was then purified and re-injected into the buttocks as a fat transplant. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 8 months after the procedure.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>204</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/mini-tummy-tuck/204-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:51:17 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/204-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented following an unsuccessful &quot;tummy tuck&quot; that was performed in Vietnam. &nbsp;Apparently, the previous surgeon only performed a partial abdominoplasty in which only some excess skin was removed. &nbsp;Despite the long, high-riding, unsightly scar, there was minimal improvement of the abdominal shape and contour. &nbsp;<br />
Dr. Truong performed a revision converting to a full traditional abdominoplasty in which he repaired the abdominal muscles, as well as removing additional excess skin and fat, and reconstructed the belly button. &nbsp;Note that the scar was only slightly lengthened, but the final result is a proper reconstruction of her body shape. &nbsp;The patient is 4 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>181</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/mini-tummy-tuck/181-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:51:33 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/181-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with breast deflation and mild lower abdominal skin laxity following child-birth. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a &quot;Mommy Makeover&quot; with Breast Augmentation and a Mini-Tummy Tuck. &nbsp;The patient is seen here 6 months post-op.		]]></content:encoded>

		<title>122</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/mini-tummy-tuck/122-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:51:45 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/122-2/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with abdominal skin laxity and stretch marks of her lower abdomen as well as a &quot;step-off&quot; scar from her C-section. &nbsp;She did not have adequate skin for a Full Abdominoplasty, so Dr. Truong performed a Mini-Tummy Tuck in which the lower abdominal muscles were re-tightened and excess skin was removed using and extension of her previous C-section scar. &nbsp;Dr. Truong was also able to remove her old unwanted tattoo as part of he procedure.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>253</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/arm-lift-arm-lipo/253/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2019 11:51:53 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.chicagoaesthetics.com/253/</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[				This patient presented with excess skin laxity and hanging skin on her upper arm area. &nbsp;Dr. Truong performed a brachioplasty or <a href="http://chicagoaesthetics.com/body/arm-lift/">arm lift</a> procedure in which excess skin was removed along with liposuction. &nbsp;The scar is hidden in the inner aspect of the arm. &nbsp;The patient is 4 months post op.		]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>32612</title>
		<link>https://chicagobreastandbody.com/before-after-gallery/breast-augmentation-revision/32612/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2019 21:27:47 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://chicagobreastandbody.com/?post_type=patients&#038;p=32612</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[This patient had severe Baker grade IV capsular contracture of both of her implants.

The patient had silicone implants placed 35 years previously and gradually developed worsening tightness and pain.

We suspected intracapsular rupture, therefore we performed  implant removal with <strong>total en bloc</strong> capsulectomies and replacement of her implants which were moved to sub-muscular plane due to thinning of the tissues.]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>
		<wp:post_id>32612</wp:post_id>
		<wp:post_date><![CDATA[2019-11-15 17:27:47]]></wp:post_date>
		<wp:post_date_gmt><![CDATA[2019-11-15 21:27:47]]></wp:post_date_gmt>
		<wp:comment_status><![CDATA[closed]]></wp:comment_status>
		<wp:ping_status><![CDATA[closed]]></wp:ping_status>
		<wp:post_name><![CDATA[32612]]></wp:post_name>

		<wp:is_sticky>0</wp:is_sticky>
										<category domain="procedure" nicename="breast-augmentation-revision"><![CDATA[Breast Augmentation Revision]]></category>
